{
  "stem": "7358.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At least the Russians considered us being in the upper class.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Subsequently, we were able, with the help of my uncle that lived in a village in the surrounding area, to bribe the Russian commissar.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father's passport was-- was changed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the number 11 was eliminated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "During the time when we had the number in our passport, we would-- we were not allowed to get-- we did not get rations to buy food.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father was-- was-- our business was confiscated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My father was not given a government job, because everybody had to work for the government.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I, myself, was not allowed to join in school the-- the youth organization, which they called Pioneers, because I was a child of an undesirable person.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When our passport was exchanged, I was admitted to the organizations, and my father was given a job related to our original business.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were actually given ration-- food-- food cards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And our life sort of resumed normal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would say it's at least 9 to 10 months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we had-- we-- we were-- we had means, so we were able to buy produce and food from the farmers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my uncle also lived in a village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a, a big-- big farm, and he had a big garden, so we did not have a-- we did not starve.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- what happened also, that they appointed-- a lot of Jewish young men joined the Russian militia at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And they-- and they-- they were very proud, walking around with their rifles and bayonets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- in a sense, there was a feeling of euphoria that the Jews finally can bear weapons.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
